Liono walks toward the messenger then stops after hearing Plintisssa comment. 
 Liono slow turns and Looks back "I Don't give a Damn what you do Plintisssa. 
You made your choices now quit looking to others for approval."  Liono turns 
back keeps walking watching Plissanta out the corner of his eye."Because it 
seems to me your care more about how me and the others think and feel about 
you than you do about doing the right thing." Liono laughs whole hearted "If 
you came here thinking power will gain you respect you still a child playing 
with toys you have yet to understand. Even I can a mass great power but what 
good is it if my spark is in doubt and it starts to become bitter and twisted 
like a snake and I have to look to others to find out who I am then you have 
your power I rather just a Lion Roaring in Night" Liono reaches the messenger 
"tell Hellbeast and Zardus that I'll meet them at the beach sector 7629 tell 
to only bring 1 other member of there team or all deals are off."
